options.query:
index=_internal sourcetype=splunkd* 
| timechart count by sourcetype 
| eval splunkd=splunkd/10

index=_internal
| reverse 
| streamstats sum(count) as total 
| eval total=total/1000
| timechart max(total)

index=_internal sourcetype="splunk*"
| timechart count by sourcetype

index = _internal sourcetype=splunkd_access 
| stats count sum(bytes) as "Total Bytes" by status, date_hour 
| table date_hour status "Total Bytes" count

index=_internal 
| timechart count partial=f 
| eval count=count/100

index=_internal 
| stats count by sourcetype 
| sort - count 
| head 5
| eval count3=count/50 
| eval count2=count/30 
| eval count=count/10

index=_internal 
| tail 1
| eval annotation_label="Anomaly Detected" | eval annotation_color="red" 
|  table _time annotation_label annotation_color
